rows.label: qst100605_msg0001
rows.name:
Meh meh meh...
It not open...

rows.label: qst100605_msg0002
rows.name:
While friends were working hard,
Nilny was thinking.

rows.label: qst100605_msg0003
rows.name:
In true Audit Bureau fashion,
we must interrogate Bahn himself.

rows.label: qst100605_msg0004
rows.name:
We will wield power of law and extract
information about how to open chest!

rows.label: qst100605_msg0005
rows.name:
But Bahn not listen to what
Nilny has to say.

rows.label: qst100605_msg0006
rows.name:
Has no respect for Nilny at all!
Hrrr grrr!

rows.label: qst100605_msg0007
rows.name: Nilny can count on friends then?

rows.label: qst100605_msg0008
rows.name:
Sorry Nilny burden you with
icky-yucky task.

rows.label: qst100605_msg0009
rows.name:
Bahn sentenced to hard labor
on treadmill.

rows.label: qst100605_msg0010
rows.name:
He not allowed to talk long,
so keep it short!

rows.label: qst100605_msg0101
rows.name:
It take much guile to trick Bahn
into revealing secret of chest!

rows.label: qst100605_msg0201
rows.name: Bahn tell you how to open chest?

rows.label: qst100605_msg0202
rows.name:
Ether Bottle,
Filament Globe,
Key-Shaped Lever...

rows.label: qst100605_msg0203
rows.name:
Insert those three things to open chest?
That sound complicated!

rows.label: qst100605_msg0204
rows.name:
Names familiar, but Nilny have
no idea where to find them.

rows.label: qst100605_msg0205
rows.name:
Sorry for constant requests!
Thank you for taking care!

rows.label: qst100605_msg0301
rows.name:
Please bring Ether Bottle,
Filament Globe, and
Key-Shaped Lever.

rows.label: qst100605_msg0302
rows.name:
Nilny have no idea where
to get them, though...
